	<content><![CDATA[const round = (n, decimals = 0) => Number(`${Math.round(`${n}e${decimals}`)}e-${decimals}`);]]></content>
	<description>Rounds a number to a specified amount of digits.  Use `Math.round()` and template literals to round the number to the specified number of digits. Omit the second argument, `decimals` to round to an integer.</description>
